 plan, then apply\n\n### Meituan CatPaw\n- Meituan's AI IDE with **Agent & human collaboration** at its core\n- Originally launched as an editor plugin in 2023, recently upgraded for public testing\n- Achieved **95%+ penetration** within Meituan and **50%+ AI-generated incremental code**\n- Uses self-developed LongCat model trained specifically for programming scenarios\n\n### Industry Trends\nThe search results indicate a shift from traditional AI IDE plugins to more autonomous **agent-based programming** tools. These agents differ from earlier AI coding tools by:\n- Having more autonomous permissions\n- Working across different environments (not limited to specific IDEs)\n- Performing end-to-end development tasks\n- Operating more like \"AI engineers\" rather than just code assistants\n\n**Note:** The specific mention of a \"full AI IDE launch in March 2025\" wasn't directly found in these results. If you're looking for information about a particular product launch, could you provide more specific details about the company or product name?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
